goal_descEN: Achieve gender equality and empower all women and girls
target_descEN: Undertake reforms to give women equal rights to economic resources, as well as access to ownership and control over land and other forms of property, financial services, inheritance and natural resources, in accordance with national laws
indicator_descEN: Proportion of countries where the legal framework (including customary law) guarantees women’s equal rights to land ownership and/or control
series_tags: ['laws and regulations', 'land tenure', 'agricultural land', 'gender equality', 'women', 'advancement of women']

footnotes: Score 1-6: 1=No evidence of guarantees of gender equality in land ownership and/or control in the legal framework; 6=Highest levels of guarantees of gender equality in land ownership and/or control in the legal framework
sources: State Committee on Property of the Republic of Belarus
